{"tha-ap9:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap9:0.2":"Buddhavagga ","tha-ap9:0.3":"9 Annasikondannattheraapadana ","tha-ap9:1.1":"“Padumuttarasambuddham, ","tha-ap9:1.2":"lokajettham vinayakam; ","tha-ap9:1.3":"Buddhabhumimanuppattam, ","tha-ap9:1.4":"pathamam addasam aham. ","tha-ap9:2.1":"Yavata bodhiya mule, ","tha-ap9:2.2":"yakkha sabbe samagata; ","tha-ap9:2.3":"Sambuddham parivaretva, ","tha-ap9:2.4":"vandanti panjalikata. ","tha-ap9:3.1":"Sabbe deva tutthamana, ","tha-ap9:3.2":"akase sancaranti te; ","tha-ap9:3.3":"Buddho ayam anuppatto, ","tha-ap9:3.4":"andhakaratamonudo. ","tha-ap9:4.1":"Tesam hasaparetanam, ","tha-ap9:4.2":"mahanado avattatha; ","tha-ap9:4.3":"Kilese jhapayissama, ","tha-ap9:4.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap9:5.1":"Devanam giramannaya, ","tha-ap9:5.2":"vacasabhimudiriham; ","tha-ap9:5.3":"Hattho hatthena cittena, ","tha-ap9:5.4":"adibhikkhamadasaham. ","tha-ap9:6.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","tha-ap9:6.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","tha-ap9:6.3":"Devasanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap9:6.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap9:7.1":"Sattaham abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap9:7.2":"bodhim ajjhagamam aham; ","tha-ap9:7.3":"Idam me pathamam bhattam, ","tha-ap9:7.4":"brahmacarissa yapanam. ","tha-ap9:8.1":"Tusita hi idhagantva, ","tha-ap9:8.2":"yo me bhikkham upanayi; ","tha-ap9:8.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap9:8.4":"sunotha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap9:9.1":"Timsakappasahassani, ","tha-ap9:9.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap9:9.3":"Sabbe deve abhibhotva, ","tha-ap9:9.4":"tidivam avasissati. ","tha-ap9:10.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap9:10.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap9:10.3":"Sahassadha cakkavatti, ","tha-ap9:10.4":"tattha rajjam karissati. ","tha-ap9:11.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap9:11.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap9:11.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap9:11.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap9:12.1":"Tidasa so cavitvana, ","tha-ap9:12.2":"manussattam gamissati; ","tha-ap9:12.3":"Agara pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap9:12.4":"chabbassani vasissati. ","tha-ap9:13.1":"‘Tato sattamake vasse, ","tha-ap9:13.2":"buddho saccam kathessati; ","tha-ap9:13.3":"Kondanno nama namena, ","tha-ap9:13.4":"pathamam sacchikahiti’. ","tha-ap9:14.1":"Nikkhantenanupabbajim, ","tha-ap9:14.2":"padhanam sukatam maya; ","tha-ap9:14.3":"Kilese jhapanatthaya, ","tha-ap9:14.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap9:15.1":"Abhigantvana sabbannu, ","tha-ap9:15.2":"buddho loke sadevake; ","tha-ap9:15.3":"Isiname migaranne, ","tha-ap9:15.4":"amatabherimahani. ","tha-ap9:16.1":"So dani patto amatam, ","tha-ap9:16.2":"santipadamanuttaram; ","tha-ap9:16.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap9:16.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap9:17.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap9:17.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap9:17.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap9:17.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap9:18.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma annasikondanno thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap9:19.1":"Annasikondannattherassapadanam sattamam. "}